"title": "5561: suffering, nature of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5561",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Since the fall, human beings have suffered in various ways. Scripture provides insights into the nature and place of suffering both in the world and in the lives of believers.</p>\n<h2>Suffering began with the fall</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:17\">GEN 2:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:16-Gen3:19\">GEN 3:16–3:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:12\">ROM 5:12</a></p>\n<h2>Suffering is universal</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job5:7\">JOB 5:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job14:1\">JOB 14:1</a></p>\n<h2>Different kinds of suffering</h2>\n<h3>Physical pain and illness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen48:1\">GEN 48:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1\">2KI 20:1</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:24\">2CH 32:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:1\">ISA 38:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:7\">JOB 2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:10\">PSA 42:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:6\">MAT 8:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:15\">MAT 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke4:38\">LUK 4:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:8\">ACT 28:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:20\">2TI 4:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:14\">JAS 5:14</a></p>\n<h3>Emotional stress</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps55:4-Ps55:5\">PSA 55:4–55:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen35:18\">GEN 35:18</a> <em>“Ben-Oni” means “son of my trouble”</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov12:25\">PRO 12:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:32-John11:35\">JHN 11:32–11:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:27\">PHP 2:27</a></p>\n<h3>Spiritual suffering</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps22:1\">PSA 22:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:46\">MAT 27:46</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:34\">MRK 15:34</a></p>\n<h3>The prospect of death</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:19\">GEN 3:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:7\">ECC 12:7</a></p>\n<h2>Major causes of suffering</h2>\n<h3>The disorder in creation</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:17\">GEN 3:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen12:10\">GEN 12:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Joel1:4\">JOL 1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:7\">MAT 24:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:11\">LUK 21:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:22\">ROM 8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev11:13\">REV 11:13</a></p>\n<h3>Human cruelty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps54:3\">PSA 54:3</a></strong> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen4:8\">GEN 4:8</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:16\">EXO 1:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:22\">EXO 1:22</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:19\">1KI 21:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt2:16\">MAT 2:16</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen49:5-Gen49:7\">GEN 49:5–49:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11\">EXO 1:11</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos2:6-Amos2:7\">AMO 2:6–2:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:1\">AMO 4:1</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:5\">MAL 3:5</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:25\">2KI 6:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:17\">2KI 19:17</a> <em>warfare</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr10:13-2Chr10:14\">2CH 10:13–10:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:14-Job1:15\">JOB 1:14–1:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:17\">JOB 1:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:3\">AMO 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos1:13\">AMO 1:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:4-Jas5:6\">JAS 5:4–5:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev6:4\">REV 6:4</a></p>\n<h3>Family troubles</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:10\">PSA 27:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:7\">1SA 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam16:11\">2SA 16:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job19:14-Job19:19\">JOB 19:14–19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:14\">MAL 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:36\">MAT 10:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:27\">JAS 1:27</a></p>\n<h3>Old age</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps71:9\">PSA 71:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl12:1-Eccl12:7\">ECC 12:1–12:7</a></p>\n<h3>Satan's activity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John5:19\">1JN 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job1:12\">JOB 1:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:6-Job2:7\">JOB 2:6–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:16\">LUK 13:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor12:7\">2CO 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:7-Rev20:8\">REV 20:7–20:8</a></p>\n<h2>Aggravations to suffering</h2>\n<h3>Memories</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job29:2\">JOB 29:2</a></p>\n<h3>Fears</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job3:25\">JOB 3:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:15\">HEB 2:15</a></p>\n<h3>Resentment</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:9\">JOB 2:9</a></p>\n<h2>Sin and suffering</h2>\n<h3>They are not necessarily related</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John9:3\">JHN 9:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job2:3\">JOB 2:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke13:2\">LUK 13:2</a></p>\n<h3>They are sometimes closely related</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:18\">ROM 1:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen6:5-Gen6:7\">GEN 6:5–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:33\">NUM 14:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:15\">DEU 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps107:17\">PSA 107:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek23:49\">EZK 23:49</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:5\">ACT 5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:10\">ACT 5:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:27\">ROM 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor11:29-1Cor11:30\">1CO 11:29–11:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:7\">JUD 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:22\">REV 2:22</a></p>\n<h3>God's final judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:41\">MAT 25:41</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:2\">DAN 12:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt8:12\">MAT 8:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark9:48\">MRK 9:48</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:24\">ISA 66:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:15\">REV 20:15</a></p>\n<h2>Effects of suffering</h2>\n<h3>Hardness of heart</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:9\">REV 16:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod7:22\">EXO 7:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:20-Rev9:21\">REV 9:20–9:21</a></p>\n<h3>Repentance</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr33:12\">2CH 33:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:17-Luke15:18\">LUK 15:17–15:18</a></p>\n<h3>Blessing</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:71\">PSA 119:71</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:17\">ISA 38:17</a></p>",
